[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_0",
    "text": "(4) 主要贸易对象：美国、西欧、东亚和东南亚.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1487680148768015,
      0.1447844685751892,
      0.5708972570897257,
      0.16584402764067127
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_1",
    "text": "(5)工业部门：钢铁、机械、汽车、电办、纺织、电子",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14690841469084148,
      0.17834814083580125,
      0.6108786610878661,
      0.20006581112207963
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_2",
    "text": "(6)工业分市：分布在太平洋沿岸和濑户内海沿岸的狭长地带",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14783821478382148,
      0.20862125699243173,
      0.7280334728033473,
      0.2303389272787101
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_3",
    "text": "(1) 五大工业区：京滨工业区，名古屋工业区、阪神工业区、户内工业区、北九州工业区",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14411901441190145,
      0.23955248436985851,
      0.9325894932589494,
      0.2612701546561369
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_4",
    "text": "3.东西相容的文氏",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1087866108786611,
      0.30338927278710104,
      0.29102742910274293,
      0.32379072063178677
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_5",
    "text": "(1)传统色彩与现代气息并存：历史上，中国对日本的影响很大：近现代，受欧美文化的 影响。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1097164109716411,
      0.33168805528134254,
      0.9511854951185496,
      0.384995064165844
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_6",
    "text": "(2)民族：单一的大和民族.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15434681543468154,
      0.3961829549193814,
      0.4063226406322641,
      0.4165844027640671
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_7",
    "text": "(3)日本东西方相容的文化的影响和借鉴",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1515574151557415,
      0.4257979598552155,
      0.5532310553231056,
      0.4475156301414939
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_8",
    "text": "①影响：传统文氏有利于民族意识和民族精神的形成，有利于良好的社会道德观 念和社会风气的形成：现代文比有利于人们解放思想，开拓进取。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11157601115760112,
      0.4573872984534386,
      0.9567642956764296,
      0.5106943073379401
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_9",
    "text": "②借鉴：及时大胆地吸纳而方现代文化为我所用，东西方文化兼收并蓄，合百家之 长，创独家之新，不断加深中国文化的内涵.便之对中国经济的发展起推动作用。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10785681078568107,
      0.5212240868706811,
      0.9530450953045095,
      0.5758473181967753
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_10",
    "text": "东南亚",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
